import NursePage from './NursePage'; // Assuming the updated nurse page
import surveillanceform from './forms/surveillanceform'; // Your existing SurveillanceForm

root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<MainPage />} />
        <Route path="/nurse" element={<NursePage />} />
        <Route path="/surveillanceform" element={<surveillanceform />} /> {/* Route for the surveillance form */}
        <Route path="/junior-doctor" element={<JuniorDoctor />} />
        <Route path="/senior-doctor" element={<SeniorDoctorPage />} />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>
);
